text: Dinara Zhorobekova is a Kyrgyzstan Student who represented Turkey at the 2013 G20 Summit. She is honoured in BBC'S 100 Women in 2013. == References == Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:21st-century Kyrgyzstani women Category:BBC 100 Women
